title: Ovary01_(Ovary_to_Omentum)
source_name_ch1: Ovary (primary site) to Omentum (metastatic site) laser capture microdissected tumor sample
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA from laser capture microdissected adenocarcinoma patient tumor samples was extracted using the Ambion Mirvana totalRNA extraction kit.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: The resulting biotin-labeled RNA samples were then hybridized with Affymetrix U133 Plus 2.0 GeneChip arrays according to the manufacturer's instructions (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA).
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Hewlett-Packard GeneArray Scanner G2500A.
description: Gene expression data from laser capture microdissected metastatic tumor sample
data_processing: The data were analyzed using the open-source R platform with statistical microarray analysis tools compiled by Bioconductor and normalized with Bioconductor's standard RMA analysis methods.
contact_department: Institute for Genome Sciences and Policy

extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA from laser capture microdissected adenocarcinoma patient tumor samples was extracted using the Ambion Mirvana totalRNA extraction kit.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: The resulting biotin-labeled RNA samples were then hybridized with Affymetrix U133 Plus 2.0 GeneChip arrays according to the manufacturer's instructions (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA).
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Hewlett-Packard GeneArray Scanner G2500A.
description: Gene expression data from laser capture microdissected metastatic tumor sample
data_processing: The data were analyzed using the open-source R platform with statistical microarray analysis tools compiled by Bioconductor and normalized with Bioconductor's standard RMA analysis methods.
